00:01:06.140 --> 00:01:08.360 align:middle line:84%
Just like, for example,
inside our bodies.

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:12.020 align:middle line:84%
We have the stress hormones
like adrenaline and cortisol.

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.470 align:middle line:84%
