00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:29.300 align:middle line:84%
You're thinking and
doing those things

00:01:29.300 --> 00:01:32.570 align:middle line:84%
and you're creating those
molecules within seconds

00:01:32.570 --> 00:01:33.600 align:middle line:90%
