00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.390 align:middle line:84%
So in that way,
every single thought

00:01:35.390 --> 00:01:38.630 align:middle line:84%
we have, positive or negative,
is producing biological shifts

00:01:38.630 --> 00:01:40.340 align:middle line:90%
inside our bodies.

00:01:40.340 --> 00:01:43.280 align:middle line:90%
>> And with these thoughts--

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:45.980 align:middle line:84%
and can you decouple
