00:23:30.736 --> 00:23:38.360 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHING] So now, the
brain's getting two inputs.

00:23:38.360 --> 00:23:41.800 align:middle line:84%
It's getting this signal
from your memory saying,

00:23:41.800 --> 00:23:43.640 align:middle line:84%
be stressed, be
stressed, be stressed.

00:23:43.640 --> 00:23:45.730 align:middle line:90%
Danger, danger, danger, danger.

00:23:45.730 --> 00:23:48.820 align:middle line:84%
And so your second signal,
a somatic signal of soothing

00:23:48.820 --> 00:23:50.300 align:middle line:90%
in the form of tapping.

00:23:50.300 --> 00:23:54.380 align:middle line:84%
And it prioritizes that soothing
signal, just the way your mom,

00:23:54.380 --> 00:23:56.660 align:middle line:84%
