00:23:57.860 --> 00:23:59.540 align:middle line:90%
She would stroke your head.

00:23:59.540 --> 00:24:01.250 align:middle line:90%
She would touch you.

00:24:01.250 --> 00:24:05.450 align:middle line:84%
Touch is a fundamental safety
signal that we as animals,

00:24:05.450 --> 00:24:06.770 align:middle line:90%
as mammals understand.

00:24:06.770 --> 00:24:08.780 align:middle line:90%
Every animal understands touch.

00:24:08.780 --> 00:24:13.910 align:middle line:84%
So say your dog, every time
