00:24:21.550 --> 00:24:23.190 align:middle line:84%
And you want to
calm the dog down.

00:24:23.190 --> 00:24:26.090 align:middle line:84%
You can explain to the
dog really logically

00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:29.050 align:middle line:84%
why running after cars
is such a bad idea

00:24:29.050 --> 00:24:31.710 align:middle line:84%
and is likely to lead
to the dog's demise.

00:24:31.710 --> 00:24:33.710 align:middle line:84%
And you can get really
super clear with the dog,

00:24:33.710 --> 00:24:36.440 align:middle line:84%
and paint her a great
word picture of why

00:24:36.440 --> 00:24:38.480 align:middle line:90%
the dog shouldn't do that.

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:40.610 align:middle line:90%
But that isn't going to work.

00:24:40.610 --> 00:24:45.290 align:middle line:84%
But if you stroke the dog,
