00:24:45.290 --> 00:24:47.285 align:middle line:84%
So the dog understands
touch in a way which

00:24:47.285 --> 00:24:48.930 align:middle line:90%
it doesn't understand language.

00:24:48.930 --> 00:24:51.290 align:middle line:90%
Same thing with us.

00:24:51.290 --> 00:24:53.870 align:middle line:84%
Our emotional midbrains
